<div class="container text-center">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <h4></h4>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Play Time Calculator</h5>
      <p class="card-text">This is a simple calculation for figuring out how much earned time the child must log in order to gain a specific amount of
      play time!</p>
      <form>
        How many minutes of play time would your child like to earn?
        <input class="form-control" type="number" id="firstNumber" />
        <br> At what percentage is the child's productive task weighted?
        <input class="form-control" type="number" id="secondNumber" placeholder="Ex: If 90%, enter .90" />
        <br>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onClick="divideBy()">Calculate</button>
      </form>
      <br>
      <p>The approximate amount of productive time (in minutes) you must log:
        <strong>
          <span id="result" style="font-size: 20px"></span>
        </strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>